main event: On 23 April 1953, four F-86s sighted approximately 20 to 25 triangular shaped objects traveling at a speed of 600 to 800 knots over North Korea.
interesting points: The objects were described as large lights with no visible cables or lines, about 10 objects were observed trailing dark colored streamers, The sighting occurred at approximately 3 miles distance from the aircraft, The flight was on a counter air mission over North Korea, Weather conditions during the sighting were clear with a wind speed of 2-3 MPH.
sighted object: triangular shaped objects with dark colored streamers
witness description: Military personnel observing from F-86 aircraft
